title: Radio 1 Essential Mix with Carl Cox 11/04/2009
description:
Radio 1's Essential Mix 
Saturday 11th April 2009

This week's mix
He's back in the UK! Its Carl Cox

The world's favourite mix show welcomes back one of the world's favourite DJ's, in fact he was voted the best DJ of the last 25 years by readers of Mixmag!  Listen out for remixes of classic Leftfield, Chemical Brothers and Underworld tunes.

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, International
